CONTROLS FOR FREECAM MOD:

SELECT = SWAP BETWEEN REGULAR GAMEPLAY AND FREEKYCAM. WHEN IN REGULAR MODE NONE OF THE CONTROLS BELOW APPLY.
START = SWITCH BETWEEN CAMERA CONTROL AND RATCHET CONTROL.

MOVEMENT:
LEFT STICK = MOVE.
RIGHT STICK = ROTATE.

L1 = UP IN WORLDSPACE.
L2 = DOWN IN WORLDSPACE.
DPAD = FLAT HORISONTAL MOVEMENT IN WORLDSPACE.

R1 = PICKUP RATCHET.
R2 = SWAP BETWEEN NO LOOKAT, LOOKAT PLACE & LOOKAT RATCHET. 
R3 = SET LOOKAT TARGET POSITION.

